#: addons/auto_soldiers_cs.wad/addon:2 input:7 standard
msgid "Automatic Soldier Setting for Military Construction Sites"
msgstr "Automatic Soldier Setting for Military Construction Sites"

#: addons/auto_soldiers_cs.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"If there is no enemy military building in sight, every new construction site "
"is set to prefer rookies and reduce the capacity to 1. If there are enemy "
"military buildings in sight prefer always heroes and set capacity to max. "
"Once a player adjusted one of these settings, this script does nothing."
msgstr ""
"If there is no enemy military building in sight, every new construction site "
"is set to prefer rookies and reduce the capacity to 1. If there are enemy "
"military buildings in sight prefer always heroes and set capacity to max. "
"Once a player adjusted one of these settings, this script does nothing."
